select count(td.id_topik) as total, tb.nama_topik from `t_konsultasi` as `ta` left join `t_konsultasi_topik` as `td` on `ta`.`id` = `td`.`id_konsultasi` left join `m_topik` as `tb` on `td`.`id_topik` = `tb`.`id` where `ta`.`deleted_at` is null group by `tb`.`id`

select sum(ta.nilai_transaksi) as total from `t_p_export` as `ta` left join `m_perusahaan` as `tb` on `ta`.`id_perusahaan` = `tb`.`id` where `ta`.`deleted_at` is null and `tb`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select `ta`.*, `tb`.`en_short_name`, COUNT(ta.id) AS jumlah_inquiry,COUNT(tc.id_perusahaan) AS jumlah_perusahaan from `t_profile_inquiry` as `ta` left join `m_negara` as `tb` on `ta`.`id_negara_asal_inquiry` = `tb`.`id` left join `p_penerima_inquiry` as `tc` on `ta`.`id` = `tc`.`id_inquiry` where `ta`.`deleted_at` is null and `tb`.`deleted_at` is null order by `ta`.`tanggal_inquiry` asc limit 1
